Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:18.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:22.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:26.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:30.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:33.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:40.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:48.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:59.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:11.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:15.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs162\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,140.389)}The Sludge Monster's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(517.167,710.389)}Terrifying Killer Smog
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... the cops are on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey— What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Make preparations for the cyborg surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now test the potency\Nof Utsubogames's killer smog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn on the ventilator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Utsubogames's killer smog\Nshould have the power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to reduce a human to\Ntheir bones in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Call in Utsubogames!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you making use of\NGel Shocker's prized science, Utsubogames?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sludge. They won't make me any sludge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important ingredient\Nin my killer smog is sludge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've created plenty of sludge for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you claim it's not sufficient?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That sludge is far too\Nweak for my purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To create my killer smog,\NI require more filthy sludge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,like that found in Tagonoura\Ntwo years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a cyborg created from a moray eel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,born and raised in the\N3000ppm sludge of Tagonoura,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,fused with a sea turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder you require\Nonly the finest sludge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear we of Gel Shocker\Ncannot produce it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as we lack the correct pollutants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to accept\Nthat, General Black?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't make it,\Nwe'll have someone else do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Utsubogames, the pollution center...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me someone from\Nthe pollution center!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Okazaki,\Nburning the midnight oil, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a biochemist friend who's studying\Nthe microbes that live in sludge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to run this experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What could live in such\Na filthy environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just make sure\Nyou turn everything off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sludge... I want you to make me sludge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me the most filthy sludge...\Nthe sludge from Tagonoura two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a madman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You possess an array of perfect pollutants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be easy for you\Nto make the sludge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come with me!\N- I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.79,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs50\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H0D0805&}Municipal Pollution Center
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster... a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's this about a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be... Gel Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Utsubogames!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I've longed for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Utsubogames, it's time to\Nput your power to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate killer smog experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're burning the fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear! I need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, speak to me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... you think your friend Okazaki\Nwas kidnapped by Gel Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a messenger pigeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But what would Gel Shocker want with\Na pollution researcher like Mr. Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not hard to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd kidnap the prime minister himself\Nif he had something they needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the hubbub?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dozens of human skeletons were\Nfound at Shirayuri Apartments!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A member of the Rider Kid Corps\Nfound it on the way back from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuri Apartments, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Headquarters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mr. Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hongo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, please! Gel Shocker is after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker is trying to destroy Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,using a terrible smog that\Nreduces humans to their bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okazaki! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him! Tell him right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A broadcast tower in Tamakyuryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okazaki, you said Gel Shocker\Nwas using killer smog to attack Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:22.68,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Utsubogames!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me, Gel Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the first victim in my plan\Nto destroy Tokyo with killer smog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, now's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the way into Gel Shocker's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly... before we're found! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Okazaki, where is the way in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grave, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okazaki!\N- What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki!\N- Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're General Black from Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fallen into our trap, Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Okazaki was... damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's of no more use to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can all die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to die, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's killer smog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the end of the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't breathe! Hold your breath,\Nif you don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just a lake on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider has escaped!\NWhy aren't you pursuing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Utsubogames.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have another option.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What other option could\Nwe have, General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider won't have noticed that I implanted\Na sound wave receiver in Okazaki's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Hongo Takeshi's apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll finish\NRider once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The pollution center and Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo. Why do you think\NGel Shocker was after Mr. Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Okazaki will explain\Neverything once he's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway... be careful, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker will probably\Ncome after him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wipe out anyone who\Nknows the secret," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okazaki. Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We were waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This time,\NI'll finish you all off together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, they have the advantage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:17:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Run to the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we really are finished with you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems it's finally the end\Nfor you, Hongo Takeshi. Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't expect this to\Nbe enough to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reduce you to your bones\Nwith my killer smog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When that's over, I'll execute\Nmy plan to destroy Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind seems to be\Nblowing the right way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I unleash my killer smog now,\Nthe entire city will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to die now, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world did you\Nkidnap Okazaki for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I had him create the sludge\NI needed to make my killer smog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:20:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Hongo... you will be the first to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Can't blow that killer\Nsmog anymore, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you handle the combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll use my final weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker must have implanted a device\Nin his head to make him follow orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if we remove it with surgery...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he'll be back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. That's a real relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:02.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider, Hongo Takeshi, foiled\NUtsubogames's terrifying killer smog plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:05.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Gel Shocker's ambitions\Nwould not be crushed so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:10.59,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.47,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:13.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Listen, my Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let us celebrate the birth\Nof Gel Shocker's Washikamigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:20.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,General Black, I will use\Nmy terrifying missile bombs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:23.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to see through our evil\NOperation: Human Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:28.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again next week for "The\NMonstrous Washikamigiri's Human Hunt."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}The Monstrous \NWashikamigiri's Human Hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:50.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:57.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:24:01.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:05.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:08.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:12.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sludge Monster's\NTerrifying Killer Smog